Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.53,0:01:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.22,0:01:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然很高兴但还是吃惊了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.26,0:02:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,其实我准备的礼物也是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.32,0:02:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,和大会姐一起挑的发卡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.20,0:02:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我也和小花名一样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.12,0:02:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,生快 荣依子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.06,0:02:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢 花名 小玉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.60,0:02:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,可以给你戴上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.88,0:02:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.44,0:02:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,小花名也来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.28,0:02:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.50,0:02:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.46,0:02:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,保佑我中限定live票
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.72,0:02:25.94,Default - up,,0,0,0,,保佑我中限定live票
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.94,0:02:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.88,0:02:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,被恭喜的心情冲昏了头脑顺口就…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.46,0:02:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,来 小花名也来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.86,0:02:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,祝愿荣依子这一年幸福度过
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.20,0:02:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,荣 荣依子?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.46,0:02:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢 我很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.10,0:02:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,花名真是好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.68,0:02:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 小花名那么乖岂不是显得我很废啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.44,0:02:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,小 小玉一点都不废哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.18,0:02:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,小玉?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.54,0:03:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,小花名真是好孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.40,0:03:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.46,0:03:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,小花名萌萌哒 敲可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.36,0:03:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯嗯 可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.60,0:03:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.66,0:03:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 害羞了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.72,0:03:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,害羞了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.94,0:03:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,呜哇 你这怎么搞的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.90,0:03:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,十仓夹子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.06,0:03:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,别这样老师 都快真的成夹子了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.80,0:03:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,十仓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.38,0:03:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.92,0:03:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,看来你觉得趁年轻就乱七八糟的打扮就是时尚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.10,0:03:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,十年后你会后悔的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.08,0:03:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不是这样的 老师误会了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.08,0:03:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,今天是荣依子生日
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.82,0:03:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,生日?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.00,0:03:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.14,0:03:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,所以打扮的那么喜庆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.24,0:03:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,呜哇 这是什么情况
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.40,0:03:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,只能感觉到恶意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.06,0:03:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,没有没有 恶意什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.84,0:03:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,完全没想「这家伙臭显摆自己人气高」之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.58,0:04:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,清瀬老师好过分
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.38,0:04:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不要直呼名字
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.32,0:04:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,总之 生日快乐 十仓
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.40,0:04:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我也送你礼物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.12,0:04:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,来 不要动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.94,0:04:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.28,0:04:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样 喜欢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.60,0:04:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,老师 这怎么看都是曲别针吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.60,0:04:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.80,0:04:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这是私人物品不用还了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.90,0:04:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 好高兴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.32,0:04:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.92,0:04:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你的心意我收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.32,0:04:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.18,0:04:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,什么 不是说不用还了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.96,0:04:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,上课之前把发卡全摘下来哦 夹子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.86,0:04:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,都说了别那么叫我了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.74,0:04:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,荣依子对榎並老师的攻势很猛烈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.12,0:04:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我喜欢那种类型的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.98,0:04:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,那种类型?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.02,0:05:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,之前呢 我对她说我毕业之后请和我交个朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.54,0:05:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你毕业了的话 我也不是朋友 是恩师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.86,0:05:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,真帅啊 这种样子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.42,0:05:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.48,0:05:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然不知道怎么帅但是我喜欢荣依子这种样子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.92,0:05:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,冠?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.06,0:05:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.56,0:05:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 在这个时间送?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.00,0:05:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,偏要这时
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.72,0:05:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,偏要?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.86,0:05:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那 来 帮我戴上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.78,0:06:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,戒指
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.18,0:06:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,觉得送发卡就重复了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.30,0:06:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,特意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.12,0:06:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.70,0:06:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 冠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.98,0:06:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.50,0:06:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,这戒指的尺寸和冠的无名指一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.22,0:06:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.32,0:06:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,老师我带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.20,0:06:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.50,0:06:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,前段时间见到你妈妈了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.10,0:06:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,让我好好照顾你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.90,0:06:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,是 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.36,0:06:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,哦对了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.20,0:06:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,学校生活怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.28,0:06:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,发生了什么不愉快的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.02,0:06:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.48,0:06:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 很快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.94,0:06:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,最初担心能不能融入集体
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.50,0:06:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,但是现在感觉已经没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.92,0:06:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,感到气氛变得很柔和
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.82,0:06:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,也许是我渐渐融入了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.94,0:07:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,与其说是融入集体不如说是你们关系好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.68,0:07:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,是 是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.84,0:07:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我看来是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.22,0:07:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,但是真是厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.46,0:07:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,全班送的礼物全是发卡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.16,0:07:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,诶 你们不是商量好的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.48,0:07:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不 完全不是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.64,0:07:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,这样全班想法相同真是奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.08,0:07:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这样的奇迹估计到毕业都不会再发生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.02,0:07:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,好高兴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.68,0:07:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,生日
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.32,0:07:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,成为回忆了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.28,0:07:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,荣依子的发卡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.32,0:07:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,把修学旅行放到一边 聊我的发卡?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.02,0:07:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,荣依子一直戴着的那个发卡 很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.98,0:07:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.06,0:07:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,很合适你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.42,0:08:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,成熟又闪亮 就是很有荣依子的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.12,0:08:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,是这样吗 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.36,0:08:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,在哪里买到的呀 说嘛说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.14,0:08:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,保密
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.16,0:08:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,是不想让人知道的名店吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.44,0:08:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 感受到了一股不能再深究下去的压迫力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.36,0:08:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 秘密就要有保密的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.94,0:08:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,做一个谜团重重的女人就是你魅力的秘诀吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.78,0:08:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,小冠 你看行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.76,0:08:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,这个人没有受欢迎也要有个限度的自觉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.30,0:08:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都喜欢荣依子的话 我也高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.44,0:08:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,原来如此 只要最后能回到我的港湾就行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.76,0:08:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,歌词吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.96,0:08:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,或者说是晚上跑出去的狗 早上又乖乖回到狗窝里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.52,0:08:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,像这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.98,0:08:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,狗吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.88,0:08:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,汪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.64,0:09:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,喝太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.64,0:09:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,十 十仓?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.32,0:09:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.10,0:09:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.20,0:09:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,就那样睡着了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.52,0:09:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 对不起 能帮我解开这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.72,0:09:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.72,0:09:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢 我借一下洗手间
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.28,0:09:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,什么情况
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.66,0:09:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,十分感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.34,0:09:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,宿醉了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.88,0:10:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,到底是怎么了 为什么你在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.46,0:10:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,诶 都不记得了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.40,0:10:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 好好走路
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.50,0:10:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,榎并老师
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.52,0:10:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.62,0:10:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 榎并的学生?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.92,0:10:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 您好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.14,0:10:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这个人才刚开始喝就倒下了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.84,0:10:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,酒量和外表的反差 很好笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.68,0:10:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,真啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.48,0:10:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,您好 我是西村
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.28,0:10:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 刚才谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.58,0:10:35.84,Default - up,,0,0,0,,啊…好 非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.22,0:10:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,醉了的样子 真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.88,0:10:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,榎并 快起来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.12,0:10:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我还得去刚才的店拿落下的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.28,0:10:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我来送老师她回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.70,0:10:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.80,0:10:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.70,0:10:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,她住在那边的公寓 很快就到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.88,0:10:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,老师 到家了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.54,0:11:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,开一下门吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.80,0:11:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,今天的西村看起来很像十仓呢 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.56,0:11:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,大概因为是十仓本人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.90,0:11:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗 十仓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.74,0:11:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 是十仓
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.42,0:11:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧 老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.46,0:11:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,十仓是我的学生呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.22,0:11:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 这个话题还没结束啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.94,0:11:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 十仓她可爱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.82,0:11:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不 并不可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.00,0:11:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,直接秒答 好过分
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.26,0:11:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,十仓啊 她是怎么来着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.76,0:11:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 你觉得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.16,0:11:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.18,0:11:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不过有一点我能说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.56,0:12:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.08,0:12:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.32,0:12:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,老师 喝水吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.78,0:12:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,那么我就回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.52,0:12:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,要回去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.46,0:12:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,当然要回去的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.72,0:12:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,要回去了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.32,0:12:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,想让我留下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.50,0:12:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,想让我留下吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.44,0:12:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,是我在问你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.96,0:12:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,想让我留下的话就说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.70,0:12:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,想让你留下的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.04,0:12:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我就留下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.54,0:12:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,会留下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.24,0:12:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这是沙发罩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.62,0:12:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,喝醉了还这么挑剔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.00,0:12:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 快休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.54,0:13:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你要做那个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.58,0:13:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,等我睡着了要恶作剧什么的 在我脸上涂鸦什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.56,0:13:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不会的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.24,0:13:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我信不过你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.90,0:13:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,好 把你绑起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.90,0:13:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,伸出双手来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.54,0:13:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.36,0:13:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不…嗯… 各种意义上都是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.84,0:13:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然全是我的错… 你也稍微反抗一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.74,0:13:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,因为感觉越来越有趣了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.56,0:13:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,只要有趣就可以了吗 你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.54,0:13:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,好像是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.20,0:13:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 十仓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.82,0:13:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.40,0:13:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,给你添麻烦了 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.85,0:13:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,老师变得温驯了 哈哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.02,0:13:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,十仓 你……
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.06,0:13:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 哈哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.68,0:13:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,真是正合了你的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.60,0:13:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 十仓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.94,0:13:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.72,0:14:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你这算是擅自夜不归宿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.62,0:14:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.14,0:14:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我联系过家里说要在朋友家过夜了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.00,0:14:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.20,0:14:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,十仓你一直被绑着才对吧 什么时候联系的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.28,0:14:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你其实自己能解开的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.22,0:14:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,酒这玩意不能喝了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.40,0:14:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,醉了的老师明明很可爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.48,0:14:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,烦人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.08,0:14:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不管怎么样 你别翘课
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.62,0:14:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,回家换好衣服以后就去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.38,0:14:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.30,0:14:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,老师想喝咖啡的话我来帮您冲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.38,0:14:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,先去洗脸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.48,0:14:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,那我顺便洗个澡行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.44,0:14:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,做什么都行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.60,0:14:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,别乱翻我东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.62,0:14:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不放心的话再把我绑起来?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.54,0:14:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,别再提这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.28,0:14:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,明白使用方法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.70,0:15:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 在家里给妈妈冲过
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.10,0:15:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,那对不住 拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.14,0:15:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,清醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.38,0:15:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,咖啡做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.90,0:15:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.70,0:15:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,老师是不吃早饭的类型吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.47,0:15:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,有时候吃 有时候不吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.19,0:15:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你们一定要吃 别想靠不吃早餐节食来减肥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.53,0:15:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.98,0:15:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.32,0:15:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.21,0:15:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你不放糖吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.20,0:15:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢喝黑咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.46,0:15:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,女高中生还这么狂妄
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.58,0:15:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,老师不也喝的是黑咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.96,0:15:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我是大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.56,0:16:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,喝醉了被学生看护的大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.72,0:16:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得挺好的 很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.30,0:16:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我一点也不开心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.24,0:16:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,多谢款待
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.80,0:16:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我差不多要回家换衣服了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.12,0:16:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,迟到的话我会毫不客气的记下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.72,0:16:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.58,0:16:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,今天我值日
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.56,0:16:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.58,0:16:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我和花名约好了要早点去学校
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.40,0:16:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你们真认真
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.46,0:16:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,就老师来说是值得高兴的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.10,0:16:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,冲个澡的话时间就有点紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.64,0:16:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我是不是有汗臭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.18,0:16:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,没啊 挺好闻的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.30,0:16:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗 那太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.42,0:16:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.30,0:16:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,学校再见
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.76,0:17:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 直接回家哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.20,0:17:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.42,0:17:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么有种本以为稳操胜券却在最后一局被翻盘的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.42,0:17:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,老师 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.64,0:17:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 一之濑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.84,0:17:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我把讲义收齐了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.80,0:17:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.48,0:17:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,花名
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.90,0:17:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你忘了一张
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.52,0:17:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢 荣依子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.16,0:17:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不用谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.70,0:17:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.86,0:17:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.52,0:17:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.32,0:17:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,真啰嗦啊 我听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.46,0:17:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,早 上 好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.72,0:17:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.18,0:17:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,做得好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.08,0:17:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,别得意忘形
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.52,0:18:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 十仓?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.78,0:18:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,荣依子?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.10,0:18:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,老师 这个 这条项链
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.50,0:18:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.54,0:18:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 我昨天买的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.22,0:18:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,为了打发和朋友见面之前的时间闲逛的时候看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.66,0:18:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,项链真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.16,0:18:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 这颜色很漂亮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.16,0:18:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,十仓?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.60,0:18:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 十仓
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.14,0:18:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.76,0:18:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,啊啊 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.64,0:18:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.26,0:18:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.86,0:18:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,项链很适合你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.56,0:18:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.98,0:18:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们去值日吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.70,0:18:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧 花名
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.94,0:18:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.76,0:18:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 荣依子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.44,0:18:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.88,0:18:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 刚刚荣依子和老师说话的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.58,0:18:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我在想你是不是遇到了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.84,0:19:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,花名
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.66,0:19:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,是…是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.40,0:19:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,能不能稍微听我说几句悄悄话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.04,0:19:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这里不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.88,0:19:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,是我的秘密基地
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.02,0:19:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,悄悄话 秘密基地
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.44,0:19:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不能对别人说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.16,0:19:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,非常不得了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.34,0:19:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,花名?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.18,0:19:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,荣依子 没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.80,0:19:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.68,0:19:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不管发生什么 我都站在荣依子这一边
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.80,0:19:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.04,0:19:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.50,0:19:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,别担心 不是那么黑暗的话题
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.48,0:19:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.36,0:19:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.96,0:19:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,老师不是带着一条项链吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.28,0:19:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.76,0:19:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,那是我制作的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.98,0:20:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,诶!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.44,0:20:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我有制作首饰的爱好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.06,0:20:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这个也是自己制作的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.68,0:20:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.60,0:20:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,然后呢 我妈经营着杂货店
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.20,0:20:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,她把我制作的东西放在了店里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.82,0:20:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那老师就是买的那个?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.62,0:20:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.70,0:20:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,那她知道是荣依子制作的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.10,0:20:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我想应该不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.26,0:20:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,如果知道的话那个人应该不会戴的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.20,0:20:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,那 那就是说老师很中意它才买下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.26,0:20:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.38,0:20:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 好厉害啊 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.48,0:20:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,听我说 我是第一次在现实中见到买下我制作的首饰的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.72,0:20:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那个人是老师
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.18,0:20:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,总感觉
